{"tid":2173721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"25歲IT男街頭噴「721」等字罰賠3000元 押後至9月判刑","createTime":"2020-08-25T11:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T14:15:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c46a1a65cb16af2685f5ae26a0950c6b44ab6eb","tid":2173721,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:46:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8656&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=53f8c6ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8656</a><br />\n<br />\n#屯門裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#張潔宜署理主任裁判官<br />\n#20200322天水圍<br />\n<br />\n黃(25)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：刑事毀壞<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n2020年3月22日於天恆邨行人天橋附近6條鐵欄杆用黑白噴漆噴上721 、黑警知法犯法等字眼<br />\n<br />\n‼️認罪‼️<br />\n<br />\n求情指被告有正當職業，被拘捕時坦白承認，受社會影響犯案，重犯機會低，亦願意賠償。<br />\n<br />\n被告需在一星期內繳付$3000維修費，押後至9月9日1430屯門裁判法院第一庭判刑，索取感化報告和社會服務報告，期間以原有條件繼續擔保。"},{"pid":"1958bb57c74b2cdc5397c02946fedba5f7c52265","tid":2173721,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"太易了"},{"pid":"0a8c515aded48678779341218c5f27534fc48b85","tid":2173721,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:10:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">張潔宜 經典</span></span></strong>狗官"},{"pid":"0488e965f9686f59dc8991687bd31e42a3c64e81","tid":2173721,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:11:24.000Z","msg":"3000蚊咁貴? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85150e8e1d1bbaf067d35fb534afe83eaed0c282","tid":2173721,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:21:10.000Z","msg":"北角同元朗啲 鄉黑呢"},{"pid":"32c8321aa6da9b4adfd523b0b95a49e731dba22d","tid":2173721,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a8c515aded486787793